        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2019-06-07 20:35:34.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nThinking about it Rashmi, since OOM and integration (including csit perhaps) repos points to API major.minor.patch-SNAPSHOT latest, ie. 2.1.0-SNAPSHOT-latest, we should have that image tag being generated as well, so to not change those repos, then we can go and change those. \n\nThe other option is to just do the changes on this repos as well if you prefer directly going this route all together.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "315e83a54de30740464fff85876d89114adf54e8",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 57,
          "name": "Pamela Dragosh",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "pd1248@att.com",
          "username": "pdragosh"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2019-06-10 12:54:55.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nI think we need to be sure to provide ALL the tag versions. major.minor.patch - let me double check this all again :)",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "d5bbb1bc3e05072e67e3688d696e7610dd270496",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 477,
          "name": "Jorge Hernandez",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "jorge.hernandez-herrero@att.com",
          "username": "jhh"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2019-06-10 16:42:20.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nOK, from integration testing, the most effective is the major.minor version, ie. 1.4-SNAPSHOT-latest, when working in a release.    This avoids having to change OOM, integration repos, and helm charts when working with integration teams in labs, which is more disruptive.\n\nTaking a look at nexus 3 that somehow, \"released versions\" (or at least versioned as releases) are in docker snapshot that don't match the same released ones in docker releases.   For example 2.0.0. 2.0.1, and 2.0.2 (for dublin dev. branch), that may cause problems ..",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "db00ecf1ff23208d2f1d56db20294d9b5992e1b0",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 57,
